I can make 'em go back in.

38
00:01:38,223 --> 00:01:39,853
(screaming)

39
00:01:43,603 --> 00:01:45,983
No, children,
you're not seeing things.

40
00:01:46,064 --> 00:01:48,614
This, my little friends,
is a schwa.

