any Jewish cowboys.

68
00:02:53,047 --> 00:02:55,047
Very good. That's excellent.

69
00:02:55,133 --> 00:02:56,803
I'm also wearing a digital watch,
but I'll accept that.

70
00:02:56,885 --> 00:02:58,795
Here you go, little lady.
And for the record,

71
00:02:58,887 --> 00:03:01,137
there were a few Jewish cowboys,
ladies and gentlemen.

72
00:03:01,222 --> 00:03:03,772
Big guys who were great shots
and spent money freely.

73
00:03:03,850 --> 00:03:07,060
I'm Mr. Bergstrom. Feel free to
make fun of my name if you want.

74
00:03:07,145 --> 00:03:08,645
Two suggestions
are "Mr. Nerdstrom"

75
00:03:08,730 --> 00:03:10,650
and "Mr. Booger-strom."

76
00:03:10,732 --> 00:03:12,732
(class laughing)

77
00:03:12,817 --> 00:03:16,857
Boys and girls, today we will begin
selecting a class president.

78
00:03:16,946 --> 00:03:18,526
I'm not allowed to vote,

79
00:03:18,615 --> 00:03:20,825
but I strongly suggest
you elect Martin. Martin?

80
00:03:20,909 --> 00:03:22,659
As your president,

81
00:03:22,744 --> 00:03:25,794
I would demand
a science fiction library

82
00:03:25,872 --> 00:03:29,882
