about encouraging him?

123
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:18,440
When Bart wins approval for making a fool
of himself, it makes him think that--

124
00:05:18,526 --> 00:05:21,066
-Yay, Bart!
-(hysterical laughing )

125
00:05:21,154 --> 00:05:23,324
(chanting)
Bart! Bart! Bart! Bart!

126
00:05:23,406 --> 00:05:26,156
Whoo! Whoo! Whoo! Whoo!
Whoo! Whoo! Whoo!

127
00:05:26,242 --> 00:05:28,122
"Nobody...

128
00:05:28,202 --> 00:05:32,002
"of the hundreds of people
that had visited the fair

129
00:05:32,081 --> 00:05:35,171
"knew that a gray spider

130
00:05:35,251 --> 00:05:38,551
